For the holidays, we are offering gift bags of small-batch sweets + savories made in Brooklyn in 3 different sizes with items such as beer + pretzel caramels, solar popped popcorn, bloody mary mix, and more. Throughout the year from June - March we offer your weekly groceries all from local, sustainable farms in our CSA with 15 locations throughout Brooklyn and Manhattan. Vegetables, fruit, meat, fish, cheese, milk, eggs, granola, pasta, artisanal items, honey and other bee items, and coffee. The Local Roots CSA is convenient, flexible, and fun. WWW.LocalRootsNYC.Org
